Source:  Press, The
Author:
Vol / Page:  15
Edition:
Quote:  Dogs which take to driving sheep away are broken in to huntaway and are called htwys (q.v.). Some dogs will both hd. and htwy and are called handy ds.
Notes:  Acland Glossary

